                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4292" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0364</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8060 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">是发现还是构建？黄薇彤的口岸机会</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Recognized or Constructed? Sandy Huang&#39;s Port Business</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">董梦杭，黄薇彤，吴学良</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广西昆仑企业集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创业机会；创业资源；企业家精神；西部边境；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Entrepreneurial opportunity; Entrepreneurial resources; Entrepreneurship; West China border areas</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创业机会从何而来？是发现还是构建？创业家如何杠杆资源？如何打造团队？这些问题贯穿每一位新创企业家创业全过程。本案例以黄薇彤的创业经历为主线，详细阐述了一位女创业家黄薇彤如何从医美生意转换成为“口岸女王”。她不仅将旗下口岸建设成全国示范口岸，而且以此为依托深挖口岸经济，带动西部边陲地方经济的发展、改善无数边民的生存状况。这其中，黄薇彤不断发现与构建创业机会、撬动政策资源与打造管理团队是其成功的关键。该案例反映了中国西部边境地区，或其它资源贫瘠地区，因国家政策倾斜而带来创业与发展的机会。黄薇彤将政策资源化为经济红利的做法值得很多企业借鉴和参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Where do entrepreneurial opportunities come from? Are opportunities recognized or constructed? Given those questions always in entrepreneurs&#39; mind, this case aims to address those questions by describing a female entrepreneur, Sandy Huang&#39;s experience which changed career from a rehabilitation beauty businesswoman to the so called &quot;the queen of port&quot;. Her achievement is not only about the demonstration ports she built and operates in the China-Vietnam border areas thus far, but also the development of port economy in the west China border areas and living condition improvements of border inhabitants. The key factors of Sandy Huang&#39;s entrepreneurial success hinge upon constantly recognizing and constructing opportunities, leveraging policy resources and building a management team. This case reflects that west China border areas, along with other resource-poor regions, are able to create opportunities for entrepreneurship and economic development in the presence of policy focuses. Sandy Huang&#39;s approach to turning policy resources into economic dividend is to serve as an excellent reference for entrepreneurs and enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家族企业 继任者</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019-12</td>
                            </tr>
